pullRequest.bodyText:
Motivation:
ServiceDiscoverer is another core abstraction in ServiceTalk
what does not coupled to any protocol and should be well documented.
Modifications:

Add a separate page for docs website about ServiceDiscoverer;
Update links in all other places to refer to this new page;
Describe how SD works, the default implementation, and how macOS
users may address DNS resolution issues;

Result:
Better and more comprehensive doc for ServiceDiscoverer.
